    "type": "npc",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "html": "A wise sage\u2019s cantankerous manner evaporates when she\u2019s expounding on matters of scholarly minutia. The sage\u2019s breadth of general knowledge allows her to speak on most topics, and her precious magic items let her gain enough clues to direct her further research. If she reaches her limit on a topic, she may refer the questioner to a specialist in that field\u2014or she may not, in order to preserve her pride."
        }
    ],
